name: Soperwillton Handbag for Women Tote Bag Shoulder Bags Satchel 4pcs Purse Set
reviews: My favorite purse, ever! The larger purse holds wallet, keys, phone, etc. I use the medium bag with cross-body strap for daytime shopping.. Holds Iphone, earbuds, ID, cc, keys, The smaller wallet is great for my cash; cute little lock to prevent accidental opening. The phone holder with the study ring is awesome. I took a small bungee cord and stretched out between my vehicle air vents.. slipped the finger ring through it-made the BEST phone holder! Wallet on the back of the phone is good quality but I don’t trust important stuff in something so easy to steal, so I put a slip of paper with my contact and emergency info.The materials are tough, with high quality sewing and attachments, & so beautiful! The vibrant red is my favorite!Great gift!
